des:
Jurassic World Alarms features a selection of fan favorite dinosaur roars from the Jurassic Park and Jurassic World films. 

Now you can wake up to the sounds of a T-Rex roar or the bellows of a Brachiosaurus! 

Alarms included in this pack:

Blue Raptor Noises from Jurassic World
Tyrannosaurus Rex Roar from Jurassic World 
Indominus Rex Giant Roar from Jurassic World
Brachiosauraus Bellowing from Jurassic Park
